			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>the earring is a must have and the peices can be bazaar bought in the 3-6k range.  The owlbear eye is soloable and there are many great guides.  Sink 2 aa into MC as well...that is FT1 fairly cheap.
<br />

<br />
The shawl is not something to be entered into lightly and plan on shelling out a ton of pp on the tailoring alone.  Add to that the no drops you must farm and the enormous time required to skill up for the combines.  Its a worthy accomplishment to be sure but its more than just acquiring ft3.
<br />

<br />
If you have the pp to spend you can shop for ornate boots which are FT3.  You will have to spend anywhere from 30-70k for them.  I bought mine for 40k after shopping the price for weeks.
<br />

<br />
Your cheapest bet is to ldon in Tak until you can afford a Sand BP and then just a bit more in EF for the FT2 chest aug.  Nice aaxp and your pulling and ccing chops will be finely tuned.</span></td>
