				<td colspan="2"><span>The coldain shawl is great and in spite of lots of tradeskills is a nice quest to do as you can solo pretty well all of it if you are 65. It's also the most interesting in-depth quest I have done and gets you really into the life of Thurg.  I really enjoyed myself.
<br />

<br />
Trial of Flame FT1 mask, very rare but doin the trial is easy once you get the hang
<br />

<br />
Solstice Earring, thats a no-brainer. Go get it, just buy the crap from the bazaar.  Its reasonable price now
<br />

<br />
LDoN FT Augs, nothing to stop you getting this apart from doin endless dreary LDoN adventures
<br />

<br />
IF you are flagged for SolRo you will sooner or later get Ornate boots *drool* very nice indeed
<br />

<br />
There's an FT2 neck that drops in Chardokb
<br />

<br />
Theres a quest for an FT3 neck in CT (Crude Bone Altar Quest) but thats quite a tuff quest as you need a reasonable group to do maze and 4c.
<br />

<br />
Also dont forget MC3 and Body and Mind Rejuve.  BMR requires MC3 and Natural Regen3 so its a lot of AA, but having good regen is actually pretty d*mn useful, you dont realise it till you have it but its a nice comfort AA</span></td>
